room_title: Escape room "The Baker Street 5: A Sherlock Mystery" by Eye Spy Escape Rooms in Baton Rouge
review: Our group of 8 had a wonderful time. We did the Baker St. room and although challenging, it was a lot of fun. I highly recommend this for a group activity. Spencer and Emery were such a pleasure to deal with. They helped make this an amazing experience
